===Etymology 2===
From the adjective.

====Intransitive Verb====
{{en-verb}}
# To [[shake]] or [[move]] with [[slight]] and [[tremulous]] [[motion]]; to [[tremble]]; to [[quake]]; to [[shudder]]; to [[shiver]].
#:'''Quotations'''
#:*'''1593''': The birds [[chaunt]] [[melody]] on every bush, The snake lies rolled in the cheerful sun, The green leaves [[quiver]] with the cooling [[wind]] And make a [[checker]]'d [[shadow]] on the ground. &mdash; William Shakespeare, ''Titus Andronicus'', Act II, Scene III, line 12.

